PrecisAppointment of John P. Frecker, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of six years; and designation of John P. Frecker as Deputy Chairperson of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board, effective April 3, 1995.
